Wood floors recently remodeled throughout multiple laundry areas large unfinished basement for storage are just a few special features. Enjoy nature from large deck and screened room. Easy commute.

Super private home located in the heart of Huntingtown! Features include hardwood floors on main level large living room w/ brand new large bay window separate dining room w/ walk-out to large deck overlooking peaceful back yard master bedroom w/ remodeled bath fully finished walk-out basement w/ large rec room w/ wood stove additional bedroom & laundry w/ new washer & dryer! New driveway!!
